  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExcelImportException  
    ExcelImportInvalidCellValueException
    Invalid value in the excel sheet does not corresponds to the field type
    ExcelImportNotAllowedCellValueException
    The value exists but is not allowed in the actual context For example a person which has no manager right is set as manager
    ExcelImportNotExistingCellValueException
    The list label cannot be identified, so it does not exists
    ExcelImportNotModifiableCellValueException
    The value exists but the acual person has no right to change it For example a startdate/enddate manager/responsible
    ExcelImportNotUniqueIdentifiersException
    The selected identifier fields does not identify the workItem uniquely (More than one workItem exists with the same identifier fields values)
